These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
House: cape-cod, craftsman, farmhouse, colonial
1. House:craftsman is on the left of House:cape-cod##1
2. Food:mango == House:colonial##1
3. House:farmhouse is on the right of House:cape-cod##1
4. Food:pepper is on the left of House:colonial##1
5. Food:raspberry is on the left of House:cape-cod##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| House   | craftsman  | cape-cod     | farmhouse   | colonial |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Hobby: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
Movie-Genre: mystery, western, spy, satire
1. Hobby:woodworking == Movie-Genre:western##1
2. Hobby:camping is on the far right##1
3. Hobby:cooking is on the right of Hobby:woodworking##1
4. Hobby:woodworking is on the right of Movie-Genre:spy##1
5. Movie-Genre:western is on the left of Movie-Genre:mystery##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy    | western      | mystery | satire |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
Sport: snowboarding, cricket, basketball, sailing
Movie-Genre: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. Movie-Genre:mystery is on the left of Movie-Genre:time-travel##1
2. Sport:snowboarding == Movie-Genre:crime##1
3. Movie-Genre:drama is on the far right##1
4. Movie-Genre:time-travel is on the right of Sport:sailing##1
5. Sport:basketball is on the left of Movie-Genre:drama##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Sport         | snowboarding | sailing | basketball   | cricket |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

