.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
Sport: skateboarding, weightlifting, basketball, swimming
Transport: boat, car, scooter, snowmobile
1. Transport:boat is on the left of Sport:weightlifting##1
2. Transport:car is on the left of Sport:swimming##1
3. Sport:skateboarding is on the left of Sport:basketball##1
4. Sport:swimming == Transport:snowmobile##1
5. Transport:boat is on the left of Sport:weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Sport   | skateboarding | basketball | weightlifting | swimming   |
| Transport     | scooter  | boat    | car       | snowmobile |

 